@Configuration
public class HintsRegistrar  implements RuntimeHintsRegistrar {
    @Override
    public void registerHints(RuntimeHints hints, ClassLoader classLoader) {
        hints.resources().registerPattern("*.pdf");
        hints.resources().registerPattern("*.st");
    }
}

Now we have given the compiler some notification of things that are going to happen runtime and it knows that those are resources that we're going to need.

